# Rule Scoping and Exclusions

<rule>
name: rule_scoping_and_exclusions
description: Apply common directory scoping recommendations and ignore globs to improve performance and reduce false positives
filters:
  - type: file_extension
    pattern: "\.(js|ts|tsx|jsx|json|sql|md|mdc)$"

actions:
  - type: suggest
    message: |
      Scoping recommendations applied:
      - Backend-only rules should limit to: backend/src/**, backend/routes/**, backend/services/**
      - Frontend-only rules should limit to: src/**
      - SQL rules should limit to: backend/migrations/**/*.sql
      Ignored paths for all rules:
      - **/node_modules/**, **/dist/**, **/build/**, **/public/**, **/logs/**,
        **/dataconnect-generated/**, **/*.min.*

metadata:
  priority: medium
  version: 1.0
</rule>

